    <section id="fs-id1586570" type="problems-exercises" class="problems-exercises">
      <title>Problems &amp; Exercises</title>
      <exercise xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="fs-id1374452" type="problems-exercises"><problem id="fs-id2420957">   
      <para id="import-auto-id3180578">Verify that a <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>17</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:msup></m:mrow><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext>kg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{2 "." 3 times "10" rSup { size 8{"17"} } "kg"} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> mass of water at normal density would make a cube 60 km on a side, as claimed in <link target-id="eip-193"/>. (This mass at nuclear density would make a cube 1.0 m on a side.)</para></problem>
<solution id="fs-id3127520">
    <equation id="import-auto-id1365916"><m:math>
        <m:semantics>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mrow>
              <m:mtable columnalign="left">
                <m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
                
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                              <m:mi fontstyle="italic">ρV</m:mi>
                            </m:mrow>
                            <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                            <m:msup>
                              <m:mi fontstyle="italic">ρd</m:mi>
                              
                                <m:mrow>
                                  <m:mn>3</m:mn>
                                </m:mrow>
                              
                            </m:msup>
                          </m:mrow>
</m:mtd>
<m:mtd>
                          <m:mo stretchy="false">⇒</m:mo>
</m:mtd>
<m:mtd>
                          <m:mrow>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:mrow>
                                <m:mi>a</m:mi>
                                <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                                <m:msup>
                                  <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
                                    <m:mfrac>
                                      <m:mi>m</m:mi>
                                      <m:mi>ρ</m:mi>
                                    </m:mfrac>
                                  </m:mfenced>
                                  <m:mrow>
                                      <m:mn>1/3</m:mn>
                                  </m:mrow>
                                </m:msup>
                              </m:mrow>
                              <m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo>
                              <m:msup>
                                <m:mfenced open="(" close=")">
                                  <m:mfrac>
                                    <m:mrow>
                                      <m:mn>2.3</m:mn>
                                      <m:mrow>
                                        <m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo>
                                        <m:msup>
                                          <m:mtext>10</m:mtext>    <m:mtext>17</m:mtext>
                                        </m:msup>
<m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext>kg</m:mtext>
                                      </m:mrow>
